OL,3,CMan threatened to kill MP and
OL,4,C'execute' NHS workers
OL,6,FA man who threatened to kill an MP and
OL,7,F"execute" NHS workers has been jailed
OL,8,Ffor three years and three months.
OL,10,FRyan Breheny, 48, also said he had
OL,11,Fbeen offered an AK-47 assault rifle
OL,12,Fand and claimed he was going to attack
OL,13,FNHS workers, Bolton Crown Court heard.
OL,15,FThe 48-year-old, of Old Hall Street,
OL,16,FWigan, made the threat to kill the
OL,17,Flocal MP Lisa Nandy, who is now
OL,18,FLabour's Secretary of State for
OL,19,FCulture, Media and Sport.
