OL,3,CMan threatened to kill MP and
OL,4,C'execute' NHS workers
OL,6,FHe was jailed on Tuesday, 19
OL,7,FSeptember, after pleading guilty to
OL,8,Fmaking a threat to kill, making
OL,9,Fthreatening communications and common
OL,10,Fassault.
OL,12,FThe court heard Breheny first called
OL,13,Fthe emergency services just after
OL,14,F6:15pm on 3 June 2024, and told the
OL,15,Fpolice operator he wanted to make a
OL,16,Fcomplaint about the NHS.
OL,18,FHe then said that he had been "offered
OL,19,Fan AK-47 and was going to execute
OL,20,Feveryone in the hospital wearing a
OL,21,Funiform".
