OL,3,CMan threatened to kill MP and
OL,4,C'execute' NHS workers
OL,6,FHe continued to make threats, using
OL,7,Fthe word "execute" multiple times,
OL,8,Freferring to the specific weapons he
OL,9,Fwas planning on using.
OL,11,FDuring the call, Breheny referred to
OL,12,Fchemicals he could get hold of and how
OL,13,Feasy it was to make a bomb.
OL,15,FLess than an hour later, he sent two
OL,16,Fthreatening emails to Lisa Nandy's
OL,17,Fconstituency office, threatening to
OL,18,Fkill the MP.
OL,26,@oD@JOUoD@ROU
