OL,3,CMan threatened to kill MP and
OL,4,C'execute' NHS workers
OL,6,FThe office manager who opened the
OL,7,Femails called police. But as one of
OL,8,Fthe officers knocked on the door, he
OL,9,Fcould see Breheny inside the house,
OL,10,Fbeginning to arm a crossbow.
OL,12,FBreheny then came to the door with the
OL,13,Fweapon in his hand. He was arrested
OL,14,Fand police found weapons including air
OL,15,Frifles, crossbow bolts, a machete,
OL,16,Fslingshots and a baton.
OL,18,FHe admitted sending the emails and
OL,19,Fmaking the call to emergency services
OL,20,Fbut denied any intention of carrying
OL,21,Fout out his threats.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
