OL,3,CMan threatened to kill MP and
OL,4,C'execute' NHS workers
OL,6,FAbbie Clarke, senior Crown prosecutor
OL,7,Ffor the Crown Prosecution Service in
OL,8,Fthe North West, said: "Breheny's
OL,9,Fthreats have caused fear and distress
OL,10,Fto the staff at the MP's office.
OL,12,F"Members of Parliament and the
OL,13,Femergency services play vital roles in
OL,14,Four communities and criminality cannot
OL,15,Fbe allowed to impede or affect that in
OL,16,Fany way.
OL,18,F"The Crown Prosecution Service works
OL,19,Fwith the police to protect MPs and our
OL,20,Femergency services, so they can
OL,21,Fcontinue to do their important work."
OL,26,@pD@WOUtD@AOUzD@AOU}D@eO]
