OL,6,FDetective Constable James Cupitt, of
OL,7,FGreater Manchester Police, said:
OL,8,F"Breheny's threats were shocking and
OL,9,Fdisturbing, causing distress to those
OL,10,Finvolved.
OL,12,F"We will not hesitate to act where
OL,13,Fpeople make these sort of threats and
OL,14,Fwill seek to secure the appropriate
OL,15,Fcharges.
